data.description: Spacious Home with 4 bedrooms, 2 living areas, 1 office, 1 formal dining room, a breakfast area and a den or sitting room off of the master bedroom.  The kitchen opens up to the living area downstairs which has a stone fireplace.  Kitchen has an attractive center island that serves as a breakfast bar and a breakfast area to convene for gatherings.  The office is conveniently located at the front of the house on the left hand side as you walk in for study and business.  The stairs are located on the right hand side of the home as you walk in which take you to the second level to another living area with all the rooms. The primary bedroom is large and features a den area that can be utilized for an office or a small media area for relaxation and movie nights. The bathroom is large and has a garden tub and separate shower with a large closet. The back yard is large and enclosed with a privacy fence.
